reviewText: You're probably watching because you're familiar with Cantinflas. Expect his twist to the classic Shakespeare story with a lot of his talking but not saying much.

Amazon, these are hilarious!
The English translation/ subtitles don't quite capture the same funny ideas the Spanish speaking actors are saying, but boy do I love these classic hilarious movies! No one can make me laugh more than Cantinflas! So sad Amazon has only one of these, please add the rest of his movies!
The 'Para Siempre Cantinflas' brand is excellent.  Always high quality items from Televisa.  Received item in fast time.  Thanks
This movie has always been in my mind, It is a classic, It is so funny. I am so glad I could find it here in Amazon.
Very funny I love to laugh And this guy will do it From start to finish
